Package in.co.rays.proj4.util

Class DataUtility

  • java.lang.Object
    • in.co.rays.proj4.util.DataUtility
  • public class DataUtility
extends java.lang.Object
    DataUtility provides common helper methods for converting and parsing primitive types and date/time related utilities used across the application.

    This class contains methods to:

    • convert strings to primitives (int, long)
    • convert strings to Date and Timestamp
    • format Date / Timestamp values
    • provide the current timestamp

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Chaitanya Bhatt
